Department of Health press releases URLs from 2017 to May 2020

Source: R/data.R
dohLinks.Rd

Department of Health press releases URLs from 2017 to May 2020

dohLinks

Format

A tibble with 360 rows and 3 columns:

url

Relative URL of press releases

id

Unique identifier of press release

date

Date of issue of press release

Source

Produced by get_pr_url(pages = 1:25). Updated as of 19 May 2020.

dohLinks
